To start a job inside the pod(deployment) you need:
1) Write a .yaml file like this:
 *spark.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: spark-deployment
spec:
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: spark
  replicas: 1
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: spark
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: spark
        image: <YOUR_IMAGE_NAME>
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
          protocol: TCP
                  
2) Start your k8s, e.g.
minikube start

3) Write to create a deployment
kubectl apply -f ./spark.yaml 

4) Write to find this pod name
kubectl get pods 

5) kubectl exec <POD_NAME> -- spark-submit --jars "./*" --conf ... --class Main sparkpractice_2.12-0.1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar


